## Monitoring Schedule

### Daily (automated — no action required unless alerts fire)

These run automatically via pg_cron:

- **Consent expiry scan** — checks all contacts for expiring consent at 30/14/7-day thresholds, writes alerts to audit_log
- **Unsubscribe deadline monitor** — flags any unsubscribe requests approaching or past the 10-business-day deadline
- **Message counter** — tracks messages against the monthly limit (resets on the 1st of each month)

**What to watch for:**
- Any overdue CRM sync alerts (crm_sync_status = 'pending' past deadline_date) — this means an unsubscribe request wasn't actioned in the DMS within the legal window
- Expiry alerts clustering — if many contacts expire at once, the dealership needs a re-consent campaign

### Every 2–3 Days (manual check)

Run the compliance audit and compare to the baseline:

```
GET /api-compliance/audit
Authorization: Bearer {api_key}
```

