**What you're looking for:**
- Score trending up (or at least stable) — means the dealership is using Nod and acting on findings
- Pass rate improving — means they're checking before sending and not attempting non-compliant sends
- Pending CRM syncs staying low — means they're processing unsubscribes in their DMS
- No overdue syncs — critical; overdue = potential CASL violation

