## Pilot Success Criteria

The pilot is successful if:

- [ ] Dealership staff can log in to the dashboard and understand their compliance posture
- [ ] At least one pre-send check was run by someone other than Xavier
- [ ] Compliance score is stable or improving (not declining due to unaddressed issues)
- [ ] No overdue CRM syncs (all unsubscribes processed within the legal window)
- [ ] Jason can articulate what Nod does in his own words (case study readiness)
- [ ] Jason would recommend Nod to another dealership (NPS signal)
- [ ] No unresolved bugs or data integrity issues

